# King of the Beach

SPA for beach volleyball “King of the Beach” tournaments (4–8 players): schedule, scores, winners, image download. Live at kingofthebeach.me.

## Stack

- React 18 + Create React App (`react-scripts` 5), JavaScript/JSX (no TypeScript unless asked)
- MUI v5 (`@mui/material`, icons), Emotion
- `html-to-image` for results download; `@vercel/analytics`
- Package manager: **pnpm** (not npm/yarn). Node **22** (see `.nvmrc`)

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm start    # CRA dev server
pnpm build
pnpm test
```

Do not eject CRA. Prefer `pnpm` in all install/script examples.

## Architecture

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Core flow | `src/components/App.jsx` |
| Schedules | `src/schedules.js` |
| Wins / net points | `src/scoring.js` |
| Sticky state | `src/hooks/useStickyState.js` |
| Per-game score UI | `src/components/GameCard.jsx` |
| Other UI | `src/components/*.jsx` |
| Brand / layout CSS | `public/styles.css` |
| SEO / GTM / fonts | `public/index.html` |

State persists via `useStickyState` + `localStorage`. `RestartDialog` calls `localStorage.clear()` — preserve that restart contract. Do not rename sticky keys without a migration plan.

Match existing MUI + CSS patterns; do not greenfield-redesign unless asked.
